Notes
============================================================

The default install uses the multilingual-e5-base weights at runtime.
If an operator configures a different embedding provider (e.g.
OpenAI, Cohere, Voyage, or a self-hosted alternative), that
provider's terms apply to their use of the service and are outside
the scope of this NOTICE.
